{"id":249420,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-长沙多位访民跪拜天安门国旗后获刑（图/","date":"2012-08-30T10:00:46Z","modified":"2012-08-30T10:00:46Z","title":"维权网 | 长沙多位访民跪拜天安门国旗后获刑（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张成报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>，长沙拆迁访民</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>人因反对长沙市违法征收拆迁，造成访民多次赴北京上访，直至告状无门，走投无路，集体跪在天安门广场的国旗下，遭到武警驱逐和警察口头训诫，后访民返回长沙。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月，访民王跃辉、李沙娜等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>人被长沙市劳动教养委员会以扰乱社会秩序罪裁定劳动教养，期限</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>年、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>个月、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>年。访民阮翔、张石红、姚文安、徐斌</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>人被刑事拘留，被以聚众扰乱公共场所秩序罪提起公诉。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>，访民阮翔、张石红、姚文安、徐斌</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>人案件在长沙岳麓区法院宣判，分别被处以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>年、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>年半、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>年有期徒刑。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>相关报道请参见：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/06/blog-post_5190.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/06/blog-post_5190.html</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-tOAd9KrH7mc/UD8xOb_mfUI/AAAAAAAAMns/XNmKTU7JBTU/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com